C IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS FOR THE EXPERIMENTS

Algorithm 1 The training of a VAE that ensures geometry
Output: the estimated parameters of the neural networks , ,  1: Train the х, , х as in Kingma & Welling (2014), keeping  fixed. 2: Train the  as explained in Sec. 4.1.

Details for Experiments 5.1, 5.2 & 5.3. The pixels values of the images are scaled to the interval
[0, 1]. We use for the functions х, , х multilayer perceptron (MLP) deep neural networks, and for the  the proposed RBF model with 64 centers, so W  RDО64 and the parameter a of Eq. 11 is set to 2. We used L2 regularization with parameter equal to 1e-5.

