For the decoder, the acronyms (DE) = Deconvolution, (CO) = Convolution and (t), (s) stands for tanh and sigmoid, respectively. Also, D = width О height О channels of the images, in our case 64,64,3. For all the convolutions and deconvolutions the padding is set to same. We used L2 regularization with parameter equal to 1e-5.

